Webex App | Separate your chats and spaces
You can organize your space list tabs, to switch between chats and spaces and pick out your important conversations. With tabs you can view all your spaces in one list, see spaces with individual people, or see just your group spaces.
Desktop
iOS
Android
Web
Click , and then select Separate DMs and Spaces.

  You can slso change this in the Settings menu. In the app header, click your profile picture, then click Settings > Messaging. Go to Space list, and check the Show separate tabs for Direct messages and Spaces check box.